  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced", 
    "date": "2001-04-04", 
    "text": "Flexibility to Increase IDEA Funding Act - Authorizes States and local educational agencies to transfer amounts from specified programs under the Elementary and Secondary Education Act of 1965 and the Carl D. Perkins Vocational and Technical Education Act of 1998 to programs to provide special education and related services to children with disabilities under the Individuals with Disabilities Education Act (IDEA)."
